Package eu.acclimatize.unison.location

Class LocationDTO

java.lang.Object
eu.acclimatize.unison.location.LocationDTO
public class LocationDTO extends Object
A DTO for receiving location data. Data must be sent by the client in a GeoJSON format. The GeoJSON is deserialized by the LocationDeserializer.

    • LocationDTO

      public LocationDTO(String name, UserInformation user, org.locationtech.jts.geom.Point geom)
      Creates an instance of LocationDTO.
      Parameters:
      name - The name of the location.
      user - The information of the user that added the location. When creating an instance of the DTO the LocationDeserializer uses the database and the name of the authenticated user to obtain the user information, as the user information is not transmitted in the request body by the client.
      geom - The point coordinates of the location.
